 Between England and France Ends","description":"Treaty of Paris was signed on December 4, 1259, which ended 100 years of conflict between England and France.","url":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Treaty_of_Paris_(1259)","urlTitle":"Wikipedia - Treaty of Paris 1259","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"Euphemia Lingen was born in 1258, in Evesham, Worcestershire, England as the daughter of John Lingen. She married William de Pembridge I in 1274, in Evesham, Worcestershire, England, United Kingdom. They were the parents of at least 1 son. She died on 1 February 1279, in her hometown, at the age of 21, and was buried in England, United Kingdom."},"et":{"1258–1 February 1279":"1258–1. veebruar 1279","1256–1282":"1256–1282","1258–1279":"1258–1279","1253–Male":"1253–Surnud","1275–1300":"1275–1300","1226–1260":"1226–1260","1 February 1279":"1. veebruar 1279","after 1260":"pärast 1260","1275":"1275","1253":"1253","1274":"1274","1260":"1260","1282":"1282","1259":"1259","1226":"1226","1258":"1258","1279":"1279","1300":"1300","1256":"1256","Tong, Shropshire, England":"Tong, Shropshire, England","Evesham, Worcestershire, England":"Evesham, Worcestershire, England","Lingen, Herefordshire, England":"Lingen, Herefordshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","England, United Kingdom":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1258–1 February 1279":"1258–1. helmikuuta 1279","1256–1282":"1256–1282","1258–1279":"1258–1279","1253–Male":"1253–Kuollut","1275–1300":"1275–1300","1226–1260":"1226–1260","1 February 1279":"1. helmikuuta 1279","after 1260":"1260 jälkeen","1275":"1275","1253":"1253","1274":"1274","1260":"1260","1282":"1282","1259":"1259","1226":"1226","1258":"1258","1279":"1279","1300":"1300","1256":"1256","Tong, Shropshire, England":"Tong, Shropshire, England","Evesham, Worcestershire, England":"Evesham, Worcestershire, England","Lingen, Herefordshire, England":"Lingen, Herefordshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","England, United Kingdom":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":